    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This folding handheld paper fan appears blank when first found, but if the wielder unfolds its leaves as an Interact action, they display an ink-brush painting of the wielder's choice. The fan must be closed and opened again to display a different painting. While held, the *fan of falling words* grants you a +2 item bonus to Performance checks to act or perform comedy, orate, or sing.",
