                        "name": "Three Actions"
                    },
                    "frequency": "once per day",
                    "effect": "You manifest the tapestry of your words, causing the image you depict on the fan to leap off its leaves. The fan casts  *hallucinatory terrain* to your specifications (DC 27 Will save to disbelieve). While this only takes three actions to perform (as opposed to the spell's normal 10 minutes of casting), the effect has no range, and the 50-foot burst it creates is centered on you.",
